 <chunk id="ch516" type="p">
  <sentence id="s516">
   <tok>
    <orth>Minister</orth>
    <lex disamb="1"><base>minister</base><ctag>subst:sg:nom:m1</ctag></lex>
   </tok>
   <tok>
